    "The reset gate r t determines whether the last state h t-1 is considered or reset to a new state, and the update gate u t determines h t is updated by the new input z t or remains the old value h t-1 • LSTM: Similar to GRU, the LSTM (Neshat et al. 2021) uses an input gate i t, a forget gate f t and an output gate o t to control the input, forget and output process of the hidden state h t.",
